    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that, but i really dont want to go to the er at 2am if it's just something stupid like gas. its not like i'm dying or anything and the pain is kind of steady now. if i just take like 800mg of ibuprofen and some extra paracetamol it should help enough so i can just sleep it off and see if it's better in the morning right? it seems like a lot of hassle for nothing",
